CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FBy Chris Young, Local Democracy
OL,7,FReporting Service
OL,9,FA rogue landlord used AI to try to con
OL,10,Fcouncil officers into believing that
OL,11,Fhe had fitted a smoke alarm at an
OL,12,Funlicensed property.
OL,14,FMindaugas Palaima sent Bradford
OL,15,FCouncil officers a photograph that
OL,16,Fappeared to show an alarm attached to
OL,17,Fthe ceiling of an unauthorised house
OL,18,Fof multiple occupation (HMO).
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FWhen officers visited the property the
OL,7,Fnext day, they concluded the image was
OL,8,FAI generated.
OL,10,FPalaima, 44, of Silver Royd Terrace in
OL,11,FLeeds was found guilty of a number of
OL,12,Foffences at Leeds Magistrates Court in
OL,13,Fhis absence, and was ordered to pay
OL,14,Fmore than #11,000.
OL,16,FThe court heard Palaima had rented two
OL,17,Fproperties in Bradford and converted
OL,18,Fthem into HMOs without the permission
OL,19,Fof the building owners.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FHe had also failed to apply for an HMO
OL,7,Flicence from Bradford Council before
OL,8,Frunning the properties under the
OL,9,Fcompany name Instyle Aviation.
OL,11,FPalaima was charged with 10 offences
OL,12,Frelating to properties in Fairfax
OL,13,FAvenue and Norwood Street, including
OL,14,Frunning an HMO without a licence,
OL,15,Ffailing to fit smoke alarms and
OL,16,Ffailing to maintain the HMOs.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FImran Hussain, prosecuting on behalf
OL,7,Fof Bradford Council, told the court
OL,8,Fthat last May the Council had received
OL,9,Fa complaint that 18 Fairfax Avenue was
OL,10,Fbeing used as an unauthorised five-
OL,11,Fbedroom HMO.
OL,13,FHe said: "The owner had leased the
OL,14,Fpremises to the defendant who had gone
OL,15,Fon to sub let the premises to other
OL,16,Findividuals without telling the owner."
OL,26,@uD@JOUxD@gO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FMagistrates were told that the tenants
OL,7,Fwere all unrelated, with Mr Hussain
OL,8,Fadding: "It met the definition of a
OL,9,Flicensable HMO, but there was no
OL,10,Frecord of an HMO licence ever being
OL,11,Fissued."
OL,13,FTenants paid their rent to a company
OL,14,Fcalled Instyle Aviation, which has
OL,15,FPalaima listed as the sole director.
OL,17,FDespite the name, Companies House says
OL,18,FInstyle Aviation specialised in take-
OL,19,Faway food shops and resident's
OL,20,Fproperty management.
OL,26,@pD@IOUsD@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FOfficers inspected the property
OL,7,Fshortly after, and found that some
OL,8,Frooms had no fire escape windows no
OL,9,Ffire doors and no fire detection
OL,10,Fsystems. Mr Hussain said: "This caused
OL,11,Fan imminent risk of serious harm. Due
OL,12,Fto this risk an emergency prohibition
OL,13,Forder was served ordering him to
OL,14,Fimmediately install smoke alarms.
OL,16,F"The defendant agreed to do this that
OL,17,Fvery day.
OL,26,@rD@[OUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,F"He joked that he could just send the
OL,7,Fofficer an AI generated image. The
OL,8,Fofficer said he should be taking this
OL,9,Fextremely seriously.
OL,11,F"He later sent photos purporting to
OL,12,Fshow a smoke detector where there was
OL,13,Fpreviously no smoke detector.
OL,15,F"The image was believed to be AI
OL,16,Fgenerated.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,F"He sent that image showing a smoke
OL,7,Fdetector on the ceiling on October 27
OL,8,Fat 10.30pm. The following day at
OL,9,F11:30am officers re-visited the
OL,10,Fproperty and saw there was no smoke
OL,11,Fdetector on the ceiling ` confirming
OL,12,Ftheir suspicion that this was an AI
OL,13,Fimage.
OL,15,F"The fire safety risks were just too
OL,16,Fhigh and an emergency prohibition
OL,17,Fnotice was served on the property."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@cO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FReferring to the ownership of the
OL,7,Fproperty, Mr Hussain said: "The
OL,8,Fprevious owner let the property to the
OL,9,Fdefendant on the understanding that he
OL,10,Fwould live there with his family.
OL,12,F"The latest owner purchased the
OL,13,Fproperty a year ago, and had ongoing
OL,14,Fissues with the defendant.
OL,16,F"The defendant showed a flagrant
OL,17,Fdisregard for safety by presenting an
OL,18,FAI image of smoke alarms."
OL,26,@oD@\OUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FOther charges related to a property 9
OL,7,FNorwood Street, which had also been
OL,8,Fconverted into an HMO without a
OL,9,Flicence.
OL,11,FThe property was inspected in
OL,12,FSeptember and a number of fire safety
OL,13,Fissues were identified, including a
OL,14,Flack of smoke alarms.
OL,16,FLike with the other property, the
OL,17,Fhouse had been leased to Palaima, who
OL,18,Fleased it to other individuals without
OL,19,Fthe owner's knowledge.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FA follow up inspection was held
OL,7,Fseveral days later, and this
OL,8,Fidentified further defects.
OL,10,FMr Hussain said: Improvement notices
OL,11,Fwere served but there is no evidence
OL,12,Fthey were complied with."
OL,14,FAfter some deliberation magistrates
OL,15,Ffound Palaima guilty in his absence.
OL,17,FThey fined him #2,640 for each
OL,18,Fproperty, and ordered him to pay
OL,19,F#3,938 costs to Bradford Council. He
OL,20,Fwill also have to pay a #2,000 court
OL,21,Fsurcharge.
OL,26,@tD@YO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,338,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1783689573
OL,3,CRogue landlord used AI to fake smoke
OL,4,Calarm image
OL,6,FIn total he will be required to pay
OL,7,F#11,218.
OL,9,FThe court was told that Instyle
OL,10,FAviation was dissolved in June 2025.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/12
